 Review comment:
   Thanks for your comments.
   Simplify implementation of `Read` in new commit.
   
   For definition of `VectorLoadAsm` :
   ```
   vld1q_u8 (const uint8_t *__a)
   {
     return (uint8x16_t)
       __builtin_aarch64_ld1v16qi ((const __builtin_aarch64_simd_qi *) __a);
   }
   
   ```
   The input parameter type is `uint8_t *`. 
   So I cast it to `uint8_t *`  rather than `VectorType*` to avoid to duplicate casting from `VectorType*` to `uint8_t*`.


